Would you tell your child
to give you a break?

58:53.219 --> 58:54.876
My mom just did it.

58:56.049 --> 58:58.914
She took care of everything.

58:58.949 --> 59:01.676
She was good at everything.

59:01.710 --> 59:04.368
She was smart and funny.

59:04.402 --> 59:06.370
She just knew what I needed.

59:06.404 --> 59:07.371
- Yeah, 'cause she loved you.

59:07.405 --> 59:08.372
She didn't love me.

59:08.406 --> 59:10.236
- Yes, she did.

