- [Silvia] But he
made you breakfast.

01:02:02.753 --> 01:02:04.030
- Yeah, it's inedible.

01:02:04.065 --> 01:02:05.445
- [Silvia] At least he's trying.

01:02:05.480 --> 01:02:07.309
- Hey, bitch, hold up.

01:02:09.622 --> 01:02:10.761
That's my sister's phone.

01:02:10.796 --> 01:02:11.728
- That's my phone.

